        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method calls the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsviewcontroller/1434431-presentviewcontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method on "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "self"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (the presenting view controller), and passes a popover animator to that method."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The presented view controller is the delegate and the content view controller of the popover. You can use "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nspopoverdelegate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " methods to customize the popover."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To dismiss the popover, call the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsviewcontroller/1434413-dismissviewcontroller"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
